title: LEGO DUPLO Town World Animals 10907 Exclusive Building Bricks (121 Pieces)
features: Build a world of animals and environments to explore with your toddler From the lions and giraffes of Africa to the whales of the Pacific, your preschooler will have fun learning about different animals and ecosystems with these animal figure toys

This educational toy for toddlers includes 15 toy animal figures: an adult and baby giraffe, adult and baby lion, adult and baby panda, adult and baby deer, adult and baby whale, penguin, toucan, fish, rabbit and a squirrel

Also includes 6 LEGO DUPLO figures: a traveler, pilot, surfer dad and child and a canoer dad and child. This set is the perfect way to teach your toddler about respecting wild animals in their natural environment!
Make a splash during bathtime with this animal playset for toddlers! The included whale floats in the water, and the fish makes air bubbles sure to delight your preschooler.

This LEGO DUPLO Town World Animals 10907 toy playset encourages learning through play, fine motor skills and creativity for kids. 121 pieces – Kids’ animal explorer toy for boys and girls makes the perfect gift for kids aged 2+
description: Introduce your toddler to a world of animals and environments with the LEGO DUPLO 10907 World Animals playset! Take a safari across African savannah and pretend to photograph lions and giraffes, spot cute woodland creatures as you canoe along a woodland river, build a sandcastle on a tropical beach, go whale watching at the south pole… With a captivating range of wild animals, buildings, vehicles, characters and accessories, this globe-spanning educational toy for toddlers contains endless opportunities to engage and inspire any preschooler.
